OL,3,CJeweller shocked after thieves steal
OL,4,Cgold and rare gems
OL,6,FAn Oxford jeweller says she has been
OL,7,Fleft in a state of disbelief after
OL,8,Fthieves stole hundreds of thousands of
OL,9,Fpounds worth of items from her store.
OL,11,FTara Hunt, who runs Norah's Antiques,
OL,12,Ftold ITV Meridian that burglars made
OL,13,Foff with gold, precious gemstones and
OL,14,Fantique silverware during last
OL,15,FSunday's break-in.
OL,17,FThames Valley Police is investigating
OL,18,Fthe incident and has asked for
OL,19,Fwitnesses to come forward.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
