OL,3,CJeweller shocked after thieves steal
OL,4,Cgold and rare gems
OL,6,FMs Hunt said she had been left feeling
OL,7,F"absolutely shaking" and "tearful".
OL,9,F"You just can't believe it," she
OL,10,Fadded. "You can't believe it's
OL,11,Fhappened."
OL,13,FMs Hunt said that, despite the
OL,14,Fsetback, she is determined to re-open
OL,15,Fagain in the next couple of weeks.
OL,17,FShe said: "We're not a big corporate
OL,18,Fmachine that has people to deal with
OL,19,Fall sorts of jobs.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
