OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1781280694
OL,3,CJeweller shocked after thieves steal
OL,4,Cgold and rare gems
OL,6,F"We've got to do everything in order
OL,7,Fto manage that whole sort of insurance
OL,8,Fclaim, the clean up.
OL,10,F"We're here on our hands and knees
OL,11,Fwading through the shards of glass."
OL,13,FPolice said they had received reports
OL,14,Fof a separate burglary on the same day
OL,15,Fat a local hairdressers, but stressed
OL,16,Fthe two incidents are not connected.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
