PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1781280694
OL,3,CJeweller shocked after thieves steal
OL,4,Cgold and rare gems
OL,6,FNeil Atkinson, Director of Mahogany
OL,7,FHairdressing, told ITV Meridian that
OL,8,Fthieves had smashed their way in
OL,9,Fthrough the front door before stealing
OL,10,Fcash from the till.
OL,12,FHe said his business will now install
OL,13,Fsecurity cameras and remove cash from
OL,14,Fits premises every evening to deter
OL,15,Fpotential future burglaries.
OL,17,FAnyone with information relating to
OL,18,Feither incidents is asked to contact
OL,19,FThames Valley Police.
